data.description: This freshly painted move in ready home is what you've been looking for in Audubon Trace.  Lafayette's best kept secret!  Walkable neighborhood with a beautiful stocked pond.  The open concept living and kitchen space is large, yet cozy custom built cypress fireplace mantle provides elegant look.  Extra large floor tiles are perfectly coordinated with     with the quartz countertops, travertine backsplash, painted walls and engineered wood flooring.  No carpet in this home!  The master suite also includes a large  closet with built in cabinetry, and a magnificent bathroom.  All bedrooms are large with plenty of space, cozy patio.
